parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become stiff and difficult to turn, making it difficult to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The power steering warning light is illuminated
the steering wheel becomes stiff or difficult to turn
the vehicle is hard to steer
the power steering assist is lost
the steering wheel shakes or vibrates
and the vehicle may pull to one side.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and experience various warning lights and messages, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts off while driving
the battery dies
the ABS brake system fails
the engine fails
the gauge cluster shuts down
the infotainment system fails
and various warning lights and messages appear on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump wiring harness can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and experience various warning lights and messages, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls
the fuel pump wiring harness fails
the PCM unit is affected
and the vehicle experiences intermittent issues with burning and melting of the case or plug-in.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the convertible top mechanism can cause the vehicle to experience difficulties with the top's operation, which can lead to safety concerns and inconvenience.
symptoms: The convertible top makes noise
the arms that raise the top are broken
and the top feels thin and cheap.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the blind spot detection system can cause the vehicle to experience difficulties with detecting blind spots, which can lead to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The blind spot detection system fails to detect blind spots.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause the vehicle to experience difficulties with the system's operation, which can lead to inconvenience and distraction.
symptoms: The screen display plan out words when the weather gets cold
and the Bluetooth system does not work consistently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The windshield fogging issue can cause the vehicle to experience reduced visibility, which can lead to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The windshield fogs up when driving
and the defog system does not work effectively.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The wireless phone charger issue can cause the vehicle to experience difficulties with charging certain phones, which can lead to inconvenience.
symptoms: The phone charger only works on older phones.
